      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so im having a really hard time sleeping lately. like i can't shut my brain off at all. im already taking like 5mg of melatonin every night but it isnt really doing much anymore. my doctor gave me some zolpidem (ambien) to help, but i was wondering if it's okay if i take both at the same time? just so i can actually get some rest?",
